Опис вакансії
Hey there,We are «Lazarev Agency» and we design websites and interfaces mostly for companies within the United States and Europe. In Ukraine, we work with«Ukravtodor», «kmbs», Lviv city council and many others. Also, we won 8 international design awards, that’s why you can be sure that our solutions are truly awesome. We are looking for sales managers who will help our customers make the right decision in solving business problems.Who are you, our candidate?
At least 6 months of experience in IT;
Design knowledge will be a plus;
English level from Upper-Intermediate: 90% of customers are from the USA, so we need spoken and written English;
Perseverance and self-organization person: we used to work with people for whom difficulties aren’t a problem, but a way to pump themselves and become better;
A HUGE desire to evolve in sales: we are looking for not just an employee, but a member of the family in whom we will invest time and knowledge. We need motivated people with big goals and dreams!
Description of responsibilities:
Preparing commercial offers;
Communicating with our potential costumers;
Working only with HOT database;
Participation in project budgeting, evaluation, and execution;
Achieving sales plan.
What can we offer you:
Cozy office in the center of Kiev (Palace of Ukraine station);
Competitive salary + bonuses;
Free tea/coffee;
Personal growth system surrounded by young and purposeful colleagues;
No bureaucracy;
Corporate profile trainings on related topics (yeah, we love to learn!);
A team of passionate people, who genuinely care about what they do and the standard of work they produce
If you needed to use google translate to understand this text — this position is not for you!Did your heart just skip a beat? Would you like to join us?Looking forward to seeing your resume and a short paragraph about yourself!See you at the interview
